---
description: Security, privacy, and compliance guardrails.
globs:
  - src/**/*
alwaysApply: true
---

Rules:
- Never log tokens, HMACs, or customer PII. Redact shop domains in error messages where possible.
- CSRF-protect non-GET endpoints; use SameSite cookies as appropriate for embedded context.
- Rotate webhook secrets on schedule; document rotation runbook.
- Provide a Privacy Policy link and data deletion endpoint per Shopify requirements.